<para style="q1">

<verse number="47" style="v" />He destroyed their vines with hail</para>

<para style="q1">and their sycamore trees with more hail.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="48" style="v" />He rained hail on their cattle</para>

<para style="q1">and hurled lightning bolts at their livestock.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="49" style="v" />The fierceness of his anger lashed out against them.</para>

<para style="q1">He sent wrath, fury, and trouble</para>

<para style="q1">like agents who bring disaster.</para>
